These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-1::.
3 different pets are kept: hamster, goat, bird
City: nizza, rome, new-york
1. the person traveling to rome is in the middle##1
2. the owner of the bird is the person traveling to new-york##1
3. the owner of the hamster is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2    |    3    |
| Pet   | hamster | goat | bird   |
| City      | nizza    | rome  | new-york |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-2::.
City: hannover, liverpool, nizza
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: july, november, may
1. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left of the person traveling to nizza##1
2. the person who's birthday is in november is on the far left##1
3. the person who's birthday is in november is the person traveling to liverpool##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3     |
| City      | liverpool | hannover     | nizza      |
| Birthday   | november | july | may |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-3::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: bus, skateboard, car
House: tower, colonial, futuristic
1. the person driving the skateboard is on the right of the colonial house##1
2. the person driving the car is on the left of the futuristic house##1
3. the person driving the bus is on the left of the colonial house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2    |     3     |
| Transport   | bus | car  | skateboard       |
| House       | tower     | colonial | futuristic |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-4::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: aconite, amaryllis, orchid
3 different games are played: mah-jongg, domino, go
1. the person who growsamaryllis is on the right of the person playing go##1
2. the person who growsaconite is on the right of the person playing mah-jongg##1
3. the person playing go is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2      |      3      |
| Flower    | orchid    | amaryllis     | aconite |
| Game   | go | mah-jongg | domino     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-5::.
There are 3 different nationalities: thai, indonesian, german
There 3 different types of food: artichoke, grapefruit, corn
1. the person eating grapefruit is the german##1
2. the person eating grapefruit is on the right of the thai##1
3. the german is on the right of the person eating artichoke##1
4. the thai is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |    3     |
| Nationality         | indonesian | thai     | german |
| Food   | corn        | artichoke | grapefruit    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-6::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, soy-milk, juice
There are 3 different favourite colors: light-blue, red, apricot
1. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the person who likes light-blue##1
2. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person who likes red##1
3. the person drinking juice is the person who likes light-blue##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2     |   3   |
| Beverage        | juice | iced-tea      | soy-milk  |
| Color   | light-blue       | red | apricot |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-7::.
