City: new-york, boston, prague
1. the art-deco house is on the left of the palace house##1
2. the colonial house is the person traveling to boston##1
3. the person traveling to new-york is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |   3    |
| House   | art-deco      | palace     | colonial    |
| City           | new-york | prague | boston |

