.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-8::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: pink, ebony, red
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: february, april, september
1. the person who's birthday is in april is on the right of the person who likes pink##1
2. the person who likes red is on the left of the person who's birthday is in september##1
3. the person who likes ebony is the person who's birthday is in april##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |     3      |
| Color    | red | pink | ebony      |
| Birthday   | february     | september | april |

