.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-9::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: parkour, tennis, lacrosse
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: february, december, november
1. the person who's birthday is in february is the person who's sport is tennis##1
2. the person who's birthday is in december is on the far right##1
3. the person who's sport is tennis is on the right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2      |   3    |
| Sport   | lacrosse | tennis | parkour  |
| Birthday     | november     | february      | december |

