.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-10::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  architect, coach, accountant
3 different games are played: canasta, backgammon, chess
1. the person playing chess is on the right of the coach##1
2. the person playing chess is on the far right##1
3. the person playing canasta is on the left of the accountant##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |   3    |
| Job      | architect   | coach    | accountant    |
| Game   | backgammon | canasta | chess |

