The people prefer 3 different music-genres: electronic, folk, hip-hop
1. the fan of folk is on the right of the person playing monopoly##1
2. the person playing billiard is in the middle##1
3. the fan of electronic is on the right of the person playing billiard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |       1       |     2      |     3      |
| Game   | monopoly     | billiard   | mah-jongg     |
| Music-Genre    | hip-hop | folk | electronic |

