.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-15::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: february, august, april
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: crime, comedy, drama
1. the person who's birthday is in august is on the far right##1
2. the person watching drama movies is on the left of the person who's birthday is in august##1
3. the person who's birthday is in april is on the right of the person watching comedy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |   2   |     3     |
| Birthday      | february  | april | august  |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy | drama   | crime |

