.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-18::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  nurse, lawyer, designer
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: prince, game, alhambra
1. the alhambra-smoker is on the right of the prince-smoker##1
2. the nurse is the alhambra-smoker##1
3. the designer is on the right of the lawyer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |    2     |       3       |
| Job    | lawyer | designer   | nurse        |
| Cigar   | game    | prince | alhambra |

