.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-20::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: lemonade, coffee, mirinda
The people use 3 different means of transport: train, airplane, roller
1. the person driving the airplane is in the middle##1
2. the person driving the roller is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
3. the person drinking coffee is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2       |    3    |
| Beverage    | mirinda | lemonade       | coffee  |
| Transport   | roller  | airplane | train |

 